                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Et le rouge Sahil, du fond des nuits tragiques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Seul flambe, et darde aux flots son œil ensanglanté.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
